{"tid":1964860,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"真男人/真香港人一定唔會買FFIV Remake","createTime":"2020-04-09T06:21:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T09:16:10.000Z","uid":6366,"like":28,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"df641b808b0c55757ff4b10997895e9afd59c02a","tid":1964860,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:21:07.000Z","msg":"本身隻game斬三份 都仲可以話加長劇情 有誠意撘救<br />\n<br />\n但頭先碌下FB 見到隻藍姜個廣告 心諗咩事<br />\n二千幾個Like 得過幾十個嬲嬲<br />\n<br />\n無人記得隻野藍絲？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人氣組合Mirror成員姜濤係藍絲？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1927510\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1927510</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都算 拉落去啲留言 真心笑左出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BhwbwT9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBhwbwT9.png&h=25c707e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CjvjFNw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCjvjFNw.png&h=7b3a0fc7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iCJdLed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiCJdLed.png&h=f6650665&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pNHibUf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpNHibUf.png&h=63828263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFF7 原來己經變成潮流game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n97年FF7 出果時 姜濤連粒精子到未係 學人賣情懷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身叫相熟老細留左兩隻 一隻玩一隻儲 頭先打左去講唔要啦<br />\n<br />\n我就當做好心 留返啲貨比隻藍姜啲腦殘粉啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真男人（尤其笑鳩人玩動森跟風果班）<br />\n真香港人（尤其笑鳩寶可夢奶共果班）<br />\n<br />\n千祈咪撚同人講會買 唔係比人笑到面到黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d39f510a3ce9bf1eb56db86f0df5bb8392bde7bc","tid":1964860,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:21:37.000Z","msg":"標題打錯 FF VII"},{"pid":"797ce10d1df34c7cf4e84d7dfe01d2dd97c1c7ee","tid":1964860,"uid":5320,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:32:50.000Z","msg":"老任就大力屌<br />\nPS就扮睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e703083cab20be4c9bca292d434fa12d9260e0f","tid":1964860,"uid":438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T07:08:02.000Z","msg":"唔㩒入黎都唔知係香港<br />\n睇個名好支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d635f53f2e3cc23dbefcc999b04325b7905cd1","tid":1964860,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"797ce10d1df34c7cf4e84d7dfe01d2dd97c1c7ee","tid":1964860,"uid":5320,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:32:50.000Z","msg":"老任就大力屌<br />\nPS就扮睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T07:48:36.000Z","msg":"真係無人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b646fc2368b6990469586a23ceb63aee6289439","tid":1964860,"uid":6366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:49:26.000Z","msg":"奶共奶到雪雪聲"},{"pid":"8e79ef91a32b786e8292183d5e47c5f6f9cbf7e7","tid":1964860,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T12:50:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3327b9299f3ff02cf93e01ea31ab20ed3e4f9781","tid":1964860,"uid":220985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"797ce10d1df34c7cf4e84d7dfe01d2dd97c1c7ee","tid":1964860,"uid":5320,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:32:50.000Z","msg":"老任就大力屌<br />\nPS就扮睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:11:28.000Z","msg":"連登 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a7b46e9b3f286e520472c129a7c25a20529fe1","tid":1964860,"uid":2667